first map and first upload :S
the point in this map is to be fast and quick have reflekses and think fast :D
the map is very small so every round would take under a minute :P
there are three main routes for each team: a route, b route, and the middle route which is there so you can come from behind meet the other team or even if the momb is planted you can reach both sites very quick. youll have to be skilled xD

enjoy and please leave a comment right? :D
